column5: CUZ I SEE YOU LYIN NEXT TO ME

"They dedicate their lives
To running all of his
He tries to please them all
This bitter man he is
Throughout his life the same
He's battled constantly
This fight he cannot win
A tired man they see no longer cares
The old man then prepares
To die regretfully
That old man here is me

What I've felt
What I've known
Never shined through in what I've shown
Never be
Never see
Won't see what might have been
What I've felt
What I've known
Never shined through in what I've shown
Never free
Never me
So I dub thee
Unforgiven..."
This... this is my exact same feeling right now... also I feel like they're all pretty busy and I'm just going to bother them if I try to randomly chat...
his tongue could very well have been the finger lmao
my head hurts trying to make sense of this
I'd be more terrified of a Maim Equinox...
